18:38.499 --> 18:40.211
Do you understand that
people could have been hurt?

18:40.212 --> 18:42.931
You could have been hurt. There
were explosives there, Sue!

18:42.932 --> 18:45.004
Somebody could have started up
one of those front-end loaders!

18:45.005 --> 18:46.428
Kids could have drowned!

18:46.429 --> 18:50.756
Do you know how irresponsible
and stupid this was?!

18:50.757 --> 18:52.781
I could be held liable. I could lose my job.

18:52.782 --> 18:56.622
[Sobbing] I'm so sorry!

18:56.623 --> 18:58.553
Yeah, you're sorry. You oughta be sorry.

18:58.554 --> 18:59.794
We already don't have any money!

18:59.795 --> 19:00.998
What do you think could happen then?

19:00.999 --> 19:03.307
[Sobbing] Huh? Huh? Think of all
the things that could have happened.

19:03.308 --> 19:06.882
Someone could have been drinking,
gotten in a car, and killed a family!

19:06.883 --> 19:08.318
- And a baby.
- And a baby!

19:08.970 --> 19:11.468
I could have killed a baby!

19:11.469 --> 19:13.607
How the hell could you let
someone like this happen?!

19:13.608 --> 19:14.567
Huh? Tell me that!

19:14.568 --> 19:17.815
Why... why weren't there
any people at Arby's?

19:17.816 --> 19:19.331
<i>Arby's? What the...</i>

19:19.332 --> 19:20.048
Dad, you seem upset.

19:20.049 --> 19:21.933
Can I offer you a glass
of nice refreshing water

19:21.934 --> 19:22.961
from the sink I just fixed?

19:22.962 --> 19:25.100
[Continues sobbing] You should ground me.

19:25.101 --> 19:26.337
Oh, you're gonna get grounded.

19:26.338 --> 19:28.524
You haven't seen grounded
like you're gonna get grounded.

19:28.525 --> 19:30.588
Whatever you do to me is not gonna be enough!

19:30.589 --> 19:34.113
This was supposed to be the year of Sue!

19:34.114 --> 19:36.669
[Sobbing] And I blew it!

19:39.059 --> 19:41.224
[Dog barking in distance]

19:42.905 --> 19:44.903
Frankie, I'm shaking, I'm so mad.

19:44.904 --> 19:46.627
You should have seen this party.

19:46.628 --> 19:50.951
If anything had happened, we...
We could have lost everything.

19:50.952 --> 19:53.535
[Exhales deeply] You
know, she didn't plan it.

19:53.536 --> 19:54.180
Still.

19:54.181 --> 19:56.470
I never should have given her
the keys in the first place.

19:57.575 --> 19:59.239
Y... [sighs] I guess I'd expect

19:59.240 --> 20:01.405
this kind of idiot behavior from Axl,

20:01.406 --> 20:03.864
- but not Sue.
- Mm-hmm.

20:04.522 --> 20:06.852
I gotta ground her. Six months, minimum.

20:06.853 --> 20:09.455
Ooh, six months? [Sighs]

20:09.456 --> 20:11.211
It's her senior year.

20:11.212 --> 20:12.685
She's gotta learn.

20:12.686 --> 20:15.884
- [Sighs]
- [Paper rustles]

20:21.862 --> 20:24.111
"Dear Dad/Mr. H.,

20:24.112 --> 20:26.671
"I'm so, so very, very sorry.

20:26.672 --> 20:28.986
"You gave me the greatest
opportunity in the world

20:28.987 --> 20:30.998
"when you hired me to work with you

20:30.999 --> 20:32.933
"and clean trailer toilets

20:32.934 --> 20:35.126
"and do so many other cool things.

20:35.127 --> 20:37.207
"You put your trust in me, and I just

20:37.208 --> 20:39.760
"hope that one day I might be able

20:39.761 --> 20:42.759
- to win back your trust because..."
- [Paper rustles]

20:44.349 --> 20:48.006
<i>"Because it's so important
to me that you can trust me,</i>

20:48.007 --> 20:50.237
- and I'll do whatever I can to..."
- [Paper slides]

20:51.179 --> 20:52.901
[Sighing]

20:58.446 --> 21:00.397
[Sighs] Maybe two months.

21:01.372 --> 21:04.532
<i>Altogether, Sue slipped 22 pages</i>

21:04.533 --> 21:05.537
<i>under the door that night.</i>

21:06.228 --> 21:09.107
<i>Mike's punishment went from
six months to six weeks,</i>

21:09.108 --> 21:10.709
<i>but Sue didn't think it was enough,</i>

21:10.710 --> 21:12.175
<i>so she jacked it back up to eight.</i>

21:12.176 --> 21:15.898
<i>Then we slowly forgot about it,
and it petered out around four.</i>

21:15.899 --> 21:17.330
<i>On the plus side,</i>

21:17.331 --> 21:18.914
<i>when the final scores were tabulated,</i>

21:18.915 --> 21:22.278
<i>Sue was the big winner in
Brick's game show extravaganza.</i>

21:22.279 --> 21:24.986
<i>Hey, you take the wins where you can get 'em.</i>

